 font-size: 27px; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">解</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 30%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: right; margin: 0px 0% 10px; font-size: 18px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; width: 40%; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appGEvXie8f8250/image/ueditor/23949800_1545732095.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(128, 101, 72); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0px 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本次课程将针对老子八十一章所有文字做逐字逐句解读，藉由讲解文本，建构完整清晰的老子哲学体系，成为现实人生最宝贵的智慧。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">老子的智慧是基于儒家君子人格的爱民思想，深入人性，了解政客的贪欲，懂得损己让利，把事情办好，所以是提供正人君子爱国利民的处事智巧，成就的是真正的圣贤人格。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">课程主要内容</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">▍</span>说明老子的两大规律：「有无相生」、「反者道之动」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">▍</span>说明老子论天道的两大原则：「玄德」与「玄同」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">▍</span>说明老子提出的处世的一大智慧：「弱者道之用」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">▍</span>说明「无为」观念的老子型态与法家型态之差别：老「无私为公」、法「无政策主张，唯循名责实」「无泄漏意图」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▍说明老子认为的战胜敌人的超级智巧：「将欲弱之，必固强之」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▍解明老子论道的抽象思辨原理：「道可道非常道」「象帝之先」「万物之宗」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▍解明老子讲述社会人才的三种等级：「上士、中士、下士」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▍解明老子讲述统治者的四种等级：「不知、亲之、畏之、侮之」</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▍说明老子所说的圣人境界：「微妙玄通，深不可识」</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; float: right; width: 2.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appGEvXie8f8250/image/ueditor/41030300_1545732095.png" style="background-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(128, 101, 72); line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本课程也将对比老子哲学思想与庄子、论语、孟子、韩非子等著作中的相关论点，从而呈现老子深通世道，孤诣独发的智慧，这个智慧，可以让人解决人际的纷争，可以让人冲破环境的束缚，可以最终实现服务的理想。这个智慧的关键就是，看透人心的贪欲，满足他，办好福国利民的好事。</p></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; width: 2.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appGEvXie8f8250/image/ueditor/50911900_1545732095.png" style="background-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 8px solid rgb(173, 163, 111); border-radius: 0.5em; margin-bottom: -8px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 30%; height: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: -8px auto 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="background-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-radius: 1em; border: 1px solid rgb(173, 163, 111); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(128, 101, 72); line-height: 3; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">唯有具备大理想的人，才能运用老子的智慧</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">唯有具备大智慧的人，才能承担天下的责任</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">唯有具备责任感的人，才能理解无为的道理</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="width: 30%; height: 8px; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); text-align: center; margin: 10px 0% 30px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 95%; vertical-align: top; border-width: 0px 0px 3px 3px; padding: 0px; border-style: none; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appGEvXie8f8250/image/ueditor/99242900_1545732094.png?x-oss-process=style/xmorient'); background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 8.7588%; background-attachment: scroll; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: 10px 0% -12px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgba(251, 205, 15, 0.3); border-style: none; border-width: 3px 3px 0px 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0% 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 21px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">名师介绍</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="float: left; text-align: right; width: 45%; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; border-style: inset; border-width: 4px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appGEvXie8f8250/image/ueditor/57076900_1545732095.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0% 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(45, 66, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">杜保瑞</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">台湾大学哲学博士，现任上海交通大学特聘教授，老子书院院长。曾任台湾大学哲学系教授。佛学研究中心主任。台湾中华易经学会理事长。华梵大学文学院院长，哲学系主任。</p><p style="clear: none; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">著作：《庄周梦蝶》、《反者道之动》、《功夫理论与境界哲学》、《基本哲学问题》、《北宋儒学》、《哲学概论》、《刘蕺山的功夫理论与形上思想》、《论王船山易学与气论并重的形上学进路》、《南宋儒学》、《中国哲学方法论》、《牟宗三儒学平议》、《周易卦爻辞话解》、《人物志原典导读》等。</p></section></section></section></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(62, 133, 73, 0.95); border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-right: 1px dashed rgba(62, 133, 73, 0.95); border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 96%; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 10px; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; border-color: rgb(173, 163, 111); border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0% 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(173, 163, 111); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">订阅须知</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 8px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 2; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.课程概况：本专栏为虚拟服务内容，一经订阅成功概不退款，请知悉。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.更新方式：本课程已经更新完毕。一经订阅，后期即可反复回听。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3.购买方式：自己学，则点击屏幕下方绿色按钮“订阅专栏”；送好友，则回到图文顶部，点击右侧礼物图标“送好友”。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></s